 Decent mix of WNW/NW swells and some S swell also showing. Thigh-waist hig
 h surf for average zones\, pushing chest-shoulder high for select spots ab
 le to pull in the S swell on tap.\n\nAnother drained mid morning low tide 
 to try work around\, but light/variable winds due in the morning for impro
 ving conditions from Tuesday's S wind. The afternoon gets better too as wi
 nds go offshore WNW for town spots.
